snippet.title: Danger Bounce [ iOS ] by Tembo Entertainment
snippet.description:
iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/app/danger-bounce/id1161377579

He is little. He is cute and he is also a ninja. Unlike most ninjas, his specialty is not sword, he masters bouncing and hopping through pillars. But he does not like to hop through just simple pillars, he prefers colorful ones.

Avoid danger, pit and holes and test your reflexes in your adventure. Chose the right strategy, tap wisely and accurately to master this impossible fast paced action game. Sounds easy, doesn't it? Download Danger Bounce right now to find out.

Danger Bounce will challenge your tapping skills and test your reflexes. Tap fast and tap wise.
